[[meta title="Across the nightingale floor"]]
[[tag books books/fantasy]]

I came across this series by Lian Hearn on a trip to DC. It was billed
as Shogun meets Lord of the rings, and it certainly started off
well. However, it lacks the breadth of either one of the epics it is
trying to emulate, though it does succeed in providing an entertaining
enough tale.

